    "id": "e4e6103b-0690-4ab1-b5ea-5f54e88e8e1f",
    "name": "Windows Server 2022 Full Administration Guide",
    "description": "This repository provides a comprehensive guide to administering Windows Server 2022. It covers essential topics like DNS, DHCP, Active Directory, Group Policy, and much more. Each section includes step-by-step instructions, best practices, and example configurations to help you efficiently and securely manage your server environment.\n\n",
